text: Matteo Berrettini and Daniele Bracciali were the defending champions, but chose not to participate this year. Sander Gillé and Joran Vliegen won the title, defeating Philipp Oswald and Filip Polášek in the final, 6–4, 6–3. ==Seeds== ==Draw== ===Draw=== ==References== * Main Draw Swiss Open Gstaad - Doubles 2019 Doubles
